column33:
name: Java CI
on:
  push:
  pull_request:
jobs:
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - name: Set up OpenJDK 25
        uses: actions/setup-java@v4
        with:
          distribution: 'temurin'
          java-version: '25'
      - name: Install Maven
        run: sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get install -y maven
      - name: Build
        run: mvn -B package --fail-at-end
